description: KHOMOintroduces it first super extra long USB SYNC Charger for Samsung Galaxy Tablet.Does your existing cable not reach your nightstand in a hotel room? Tired of the short standard cord? Finally, a solution! With our 6 foot cable there will be no more leaning close to your outlet to use your tablet. It is convenient, easy to use, and 100% compatible with the existing Samsung Tablets (7 and 10.1 models). With high-quality and sturdy engineering, this cable is a must have for in your home, car, traveling, and more.
title: KHOMO Super Long 6ft (SIX Feet!) USB Data Charging Cable for Samsung Galaxy Tab
